StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@SMCRReserveUnitID uniqueiden..er, @CollegePro.leID uniqueiden..er, @UserLogin varchar(50)
AS SET NOCOUNT ON
DECLARE @CollegeName varchar(60)
IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT '1' from [MCRISS].[USMC].[CollegePro.leSMCRReserveUnit]
where SMCRReserveUnitID = @SMCRReserveUnitID and @SMCRReserveUnitID IS NOT NULL and CollegePro.leID = @CollegePro.leID and @CollegePro.leID IS NOT NULL)
BEGIN
INSERT INTO [MCRISS].[USMC].[CollegePro.leSMCRReserveUnit] ( [SMCRReserveUnitID] ,[CollegePro.leID] ,[UserLogin] ,[UpdateDate] ) VALUES ( @SMCRReserveUnitID, @CollegePro.leID, @UserLogin, GetDate() )
END
